headline: Trimble Becomes Official Global Partner with Liverpool Football Club
summary: Trimble (Nasdaq: TRMB) today announced a new multi-year global sponsorship with Liverpool Football Club (LFC), marking a significant expansion of Trimble's global sports marketing strategy. This collaboration is driven by shared values of precision, innovation and a commitment to transforming how work gets done — both on and off the pitch.
